Insider Activity


Individual




Alan M. Bennett



Mr. Alan M. Bennett, CPA, is Independent Director at Fluor Corp., Independent Director at The TJX Cos., Inc., Independent Director at Halliburton Co., and a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. He is on the Board of Directors at Fluor Corp., The TJX Cos., Inc., and Halliburton Co.
Mr. Bennett was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by H&R Block, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Aetna Business Resources, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Aetna, Inc., Vice President-Sales & Marketing by Armstrong Tire Corp., Vice President-Sales & Marketing by Pirelli Armstrong Tire Corp., Audit Manager by Ernst & Young LLP, and Chief Executive Officer by H&R Block Financial Advisors. He also served on the board at Bausch & Lomb, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Susquehanna University.



